			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				You have to agree to the license agreement before you can use the registration key. One of the things you agree to is that the account is non-transferable. One the registration key is used, it's worthless...the account is not IN the box you bought, it's in a sony computer in their server room. You own the box and the discs, but you're SOL on the account itself. In practice, you can use it, but remember the original owner can attempt to reclaim it, or at the very least have it banned at his discretion. My advice to you if you're building a serious character is to go buy a legitimate box.<BR>
<BR>
Oh, and you must enter a credit card to use the free month, but the card is NOT charged until the free month is gone.
